    #submit.step1(style="background-size:cover;")
      .container
        .row
          .col-md-1.text-right
            h1#one 1
          .col-md-5
            h2 Submit Your Design Idea
            h3 Get Inspired and Tell Us What You Want to Make
            p(id="quote").
               Fill out a design brief and add pictures and/or sketches to an Idea Board to communicate the vision for your product. If you need some inspiration, let us know, we can help!
          .col-md-6.text-center(id="mac")
            a(href="#modal1", data-target="#modal1", role="modal", data-toggle="modal")
              img(src='icons/submit_your_idea_imac.png')
    #meet.step2
      .container
        .row
          .col-md-1.text-left(id="header2")
            h1 2
          .col-md-6.text-center
            img(src='icons/Start_collaborating_Imac.png')
          .col-md-5
            h2.text-right Start Collaborating
            h3.text-right Meet Your Designer and Start Your Project
            p.text-right#mobile We will assign you a designer from our network of world-class product designers. Once you start your project, you will be directed to our design center where you&apos;ll communicate directly with your designer.
          
    #view.step3(style="background-size:cover;")
      .container
        .row
          .col-md-1.text-right
            h1#three 3
          .col-md-5
            h2 View Digital Preview
            h3 Bring Your Idea to Life on Screen Before Making Your Order
            p#quote As soon as you and your designer agree on a design, your designer will send across a life-like digital preview of your product. Iterate on your product design until you are in love.
          .col-md-6.text-center
            img(src='icons/view_digital_product.png')
    #hold.step4
      .container
        .row
          .col-md-1.text-left
            h1 4
          .col-md-6.text-center
            img(src='icons/holdinyourhandimac.png')
          .col-md-5
